div.div:
«dict» _pending_futures
{user_id → asyncio.Future}
created by _send_command_tagged;
resolved + popped by _response_reader;
cleared on model reload or leave

«dict» _stream_queues:
each is a queue of metadata that tell the consumer which part of the shared
stream buffer to read next.
{user_id → asyncio.Queue}
created by register_stream_queue()
written by _response_reader (MediaInit / Chunk / Complete);
consumed by AV loop → ws.send_bytes / send_json;
popped by leave_user(); cleared on reload
